vent emissions for admin/config changes.\n- Good separation of concerns between AML, conversion, and admin logic.\n- Foundry/CI configuration is robust and up-to-date.\n\nImplementing the above minimal safeguards and tests will significantly improve the safety and reliability of the hook, especially for demonstration or limited production use.",
